title: Upon Payment of 100% premium as foresaid, C
clause_text: Upon Payment of 100% premium as foresaid, C.C. shall be issued in respect of 50% of incentive FSI. In no case, shall the remaining 50% Incentive FSI be released without the handing over of the PPL, complete in all respects, to MCGM.
